data.description: Check out this amzing ly located Atrium split home in South Grandview! You will love the curb appear of this home from the moment you pull up. The stone wrapped mail box, covered front porch, and extended 3 car driveway are some of the awesome features youll notice at first. Once inside you will love the lawout offering space for everyone! The main floor sitting room offers vaulted ceilings, fireplace, and openess to the kitchen and dining room. The kitchen is well layed out and offers a walk in pantry, granite, and stainless appliances. The dining room walks out back to the deck. Upstairs you will find the laundry room along with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The owners suite has a large walk in closet along with a generouse bathroom. The lower level offers a 1/2 bath and a large rec space that walks out to the covered patio! The subbeasement is a great fourth non conforming room or recreation space. There is a stunning built in, egress window, and large space. You will even like the storage and storm shelter. Out back enjoy the entertainment spaces and fenced in yard. This home is situated in a convenient and quite neighborhood.
